The ''disjoint union'' of two {{topsps}} $$X$$ and $$Y$$ is denoted $$X \amalg Y$$ and is given by

* The [[Point]]s are the [[Disjoint Union]] $$X \amalg Y$$
* A [[Subset]] $$U \subseteq X \amalg Y$$ is [[Open|Open Set]] if and only if $$U \cap X$$ and $$U \cap Y$$ are open.